            </button>
            </form>
            <p>Steam profile example: https://steamcommunity.com/id/gergelyszabo/</p>
            <p>Trade link example: https://steamcommunity.com/tradeoffer/new/?partner=75764727&token=tx0asz7q</p>
            <p>Or check an inventory directly <a href="/inventory/76561198036030455">by link</a>.</p>
            <br>
            <p>
                What is a trade lock? At the end of March of 2018 Valve implemented a <a target="_blank" href="http://blog.counter-strike.net/index.php/2018/03/20308/">new update to CS:GO trading</a>.
                They restrict the trading of newly received items by locking them to the account for 7 days.
                Once an inventory is loaded there is a countdown displayed for every item that marks the end of this seven-day trade cooldown.
            </p>

            <div id="error">
                <span>{{error}}</span>
            </div>
